20so%20investors%20will%20be%20looking%20for%20clues%20as%20to%20how%20companies%20are%20progressing%20in%20monetizing%20their%20AI%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20the%20question%20of%20sectors%20other%20than%20tech%20where%20AI%20may%20be%20having%20an%20impact.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20big%20driver%20of%20future%20growth%20is%20going%20to%20hinge%20on%20how%20the%20applications%20of%20AI%20will%20be%20broadening%20out%20into%20other%20sectors%20such%20as%20Healthcare%2C%20Industrials%2C%20and%20Aerospace%20and%20Defense.%20These%20are%20sectors%20that%20are%20most%20likely%20to%20be%20phase%20two%20beneficiaries%20of%20this%20crucial%20technology%20beyond%20chip%20makers%20and%20data%20centers%2C%26quot%3B%20Horizon%20Investments'%20Dickson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ac3f2d29-9ffa-4a02-8886-d18e86e36f86%5C%22%3EConsumer%20health%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fally-financial-stock-price-plunges-cfo-says-consumer-pressures-intensifying-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20worrying%20update%20from%20lending%20giant%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ally%20Financial%20in%20September%20and%20fears%20of%20a%20spending%20slowdown%20as%20pandemic%20savings%20dry%20up%2C%20investors%20will%20be%20keenly%20focused%20on%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20consumer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20be%20important%20to%20keep%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20what%20the%20banks%20say%20about%20credit%20delinquencies%20and%20loan%20quality%2C%20along%20with%20the%20retail-focused%20firms%20and%20what%20they%20see%20in%20consumer%20spending%20behavior.%20GDP-related%20data%20shows%20strong%20trends%20here%20but%20more%20timely%20and%20granular%20views%20will%20be%20in%20focus%2C%26quot%3B%20Dickson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHainlin%20said%20he%20is%20encouraged%20by%20continued%20growth%20in%20consumer%20spending%20as%20credit%20card%20defaults%20%26quot%3Bare%20within%20normal%20levels%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20holiday%20shopping%20season%20is%20right%20around%20the%20corner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20some%20warning%20signs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20travel%20remains%20strong%2C%20overall%20experiences%20spending%20appears%20to%20have%20plateaued%20with%20consumers%20redirecting%20or%20broadening%20spending%20in%20other%20sectors.%20Additionally%2C%20lower-income%20groups%20are%20exhibiting%20signs%20of%20financial%20stress%20and%20slowing%20overall%20spending%2C%26quot%3B%20Hainlin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarnings%20guidance%20from%20banks%2C%20retailers%2C%20and%20consumer%20discretionary%20companies%20should%20offer%20the%20granular%20views%20that%20will%20help%20investors%20assess%20what%20to%20expect%20from%20the%20consumer%20heading%20into%20year-end%20and%20in%202025.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2214095169-d8ee-47c5-81bf-dd9fe87396b8%5C%22%3EThe%20impact%20of%20lower%20interest%20rates%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20delivering%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseptember-jobs-report-fed-rate-cut-outlook-november-labor-market-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eits%20first%20interest%20rate%20cut%20of%20the%20cycle%20at%20the%20end%20of%20last%20quarter%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20investors%20will%20want%20to%20see%20if%20lower%20capital%20costs%20have%20trickled%20down%20into%20company%20results%20and%2For%20their%20guidance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spotlight%20will%20be%20on%20rate-sensitive%20sectors%2C%20like%20banks%20and%20utilities%2C%20as%20well%20as%20smaller-sized%20companies%20which%20tend%20to%20carry%20more%20debt%2C%20according%20to%20Dickson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20be%20key%20to%20see%20how%20mid%20and%20small-cap%20companies%20respond%20to%20falling%20rates%20that%20we've%20seen%20over%20the%20third%20quarter.%20These%20firms%20were%20hurt%20a%20lot%20on%20a%20relative%20basis%20so%20if%20they%20discuss%20a%20meaningful%20reduction%20in%20debt%