eplace%20always%20reflect%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fimpress-boss-prioritize-impactful-work-2018-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ededication%20to%20the%20organization's%20mission%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20they%20can%20also%20come%20across%20in%20a%20less%20desirable%20way%20depending%20on%20how%20or%20what%20you%20are%20applying%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20a%20recruiter%20or%20hiring%20manager%20sees%20you%20have%20applied%20to%20multiple%20roles%20for%20one%20company%2C%20especially%20roles%20that%20are%20all%20very%20different%2C%20it%20can%20raise%20concerns%20that%20you%20may%20lack%20a%20clear%20focus%20or%20are%20just%20looking%20for%20any%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indeed.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndeed%3C%2Fa%3E%20career%20trends%20expert%20Gabby%20Davis.%20%26quot%3BEmployers%20may%20wonder%20about%20your%20commitment%20or%20suitability%20for%20specific%20roles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavis%20notes%20it's%20%26quot%3Bgenerally%20not%20recommended%20to%20apply%20to%20the%20same%20employer%20more%20than%20twice%20for%20the%20same%20position%20if%20you've%20been%20rejected%20or%20received%20no%20response%2C%20especially%20if%20your%20qualifications%20have%20not%20changed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2202539de7-d6e0-4054-b138-3dc5acccb496%5C%22%3EFocus%20on%20new%20skills%20and%20experience%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20should%20consider%20reapplying%20somewhere%2C%20however%2C%20%26quot%3Bif%20you've%20significantly%20improved%20your%20skills%2C%20expanded%20your%20portfolio%2C%20or%20built%20sufficient%20relationships%20within%20the%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Cynthia%20Pong%2C%20an%20executive%20coach%2C%20speaker%2C%20and%20founder%20of%20career%20coaching%20and%20training%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.embracechange.nyc%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEmbrace%20Change%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20employers%20have%20guidelines%20around%20how%20soon%20you%20can%20reapply%20after%20being%20rejected%2C%20notes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.farahsharghi.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFarah%20Sharghi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20career%20coach%20and%20strategist%20and%20former%20tech%20recruiter.%20Sharghi%20advises%20waiting%20at%20least%203%20to%206%20months%20after%20being%20rejected%20to%20reapply%20unless%20the%20company%20explicitly%20invites%20you%20to%20apply%20for%20other%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20do%20reapply%2C%20make%20sure%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-tailor-your-resume-for-job-applications-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etweak%20your%20application%20materials%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20what%20you%20submitted%20before%20so%20they%20reflect%20how%20you've%20learned%20and%20grown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBe%20sure%20to%20emphasize%20new%20skills%2C%20experiences%2C%20or%20achievements%20since%20your%20last%20application%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Pong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22952cbfe1-4774-401f-aa92-e376b746087c%5C%22%3EEmphasize%20your%20interest%20in%20the%20employer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20offered%20an%20interview%2C%20%26quot%3Bbe%20honest%20and%20frame%20it%20positively%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Sharghi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20script%20Sharghi%20suggests%3A%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20I've%20applied%20to%20a%20few%20positions%20here%20because%20I'm%20genuinely%20excited%20about%20the%20company's%20mission%20and%20culture.%20Each%20role%20I've%20applied%20for%20aligns%20with%20my%20skills%20and%20career%20goals%20in%20different%20ways.%20For%20this%20specific%20position%2C%20I'm%20particularly%20interested%20because%20%5Bmention%20specific%20aspects%20of%20the%20job%20that%20appeal%20to%20you%5D.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20focusing%20on%20what%20new%20skills%20you%20bring%20to%20the%20table%20now%2C%20and%20honing%20in%20on%20your%20interest%20in%20the%20company%2