elated%20deaths%20this%20year%2C%20including%2017%20since%20January.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Funprecedented-savegery-prosecutor-claims-15-year-teenager-stabbed-50-times-and-burned-alive-likely-in-drug-related-attack%2Farticleshow%2F113985429.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Funprecedented-savegery-prosecutor-claims-15-year-teenager-stabbed-50-times-and-burned-alive-likely-in-drug-related-attack%2Famp_articleshow%2F113985429.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Funprecedented-savegery-prosecutor-claims-15-year-teenager-stabbed-50-times-and-burned-alive-likely-in-drug-related-attack%2Famp_articleshow%2F113985429.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20worked%20as%20a%20wealth%20advisor%20for%20Goldman%20Sachs.%20Here's%20what%20I%20learned%20from%20how%20the%20super%20rich%20manage%20their%20money.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226576%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20in%20a%20white%20jacket%20outside%20a%20white%20house%20with%20railings.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fd6c7d9e0c5c2eeeea095e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224384%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAyesha%20Ofori%20was%20a%20wealth%20advisor%20for%20Goldman%20Sachs.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Yolande%20De%20Vries%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAyesha%20Ofori%20worked%20in%20wealth%20management%20for%20Goldman%20Sachs%20for%20six%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20told%20Business%20Insider%20she%20left%20to%20start%20her%20own%20business%2C%20an%20investment%20platform%20for%20women.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOfori%20shared%20wealth-building%20strategies%20she%20learned%20from%20managing%20her%20ultrawealthy%20clients'%20portfolios.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20transcribed%20conversation%20with%2040-year-old%20Ayesha%20Ofori%2C%20CEO%20of%20Propelle%2C%20from%20London%2C%20about%20her%20experience%20working%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20her%20employment.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20joined%20Goldman%20Sachs%20in%20New%20York%20in%20July%202012.%20Before%20that%2C%20I'd%20studied%20for%20an%20MBA%20at%20Columbia%20Business%20School.%20While%20there%2C%20I%20interned%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20my%20training%20in%20wealth%20management%20in%20New%20York%20in%20September%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20London%20to%20work%20at%20Goldman's%20UK%20office%20in%20wealth%20management.%20If%20you're%20in%20banking%2C%20there's%20nowhere%20bigger.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you'd%20asked%20me%20what%20success%20looked%20like%20at%20the%20time%2C%20it%20would've%20been%20being%20a%20partner%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs.%20The%20culture%20suited%20me%20because%20I'm%20an%20alpha.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20years%20later%2C%20I%20quit%20to%20start%20my%20own%20business%2C%20helping%20women%20close%20the%20investment%20gap.%20At%20Goldman%2C%20I%20helped%20rich%20men%20get%20richer%2C%20but%20I%20also%20learned%20lessons%20about%20wealth%20management%20from%20Goldman%20and%20my%20own%20experience%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20share.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224c882070-3e42-49b5-9360-716579a820e3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20clients%20I%20managed%20often%20had%20over%20%2410%20million%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20wealth%20manager%2C%20I%20looked%20after%20individuals'%20private%20wealth.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20job%20was%20to%20find%20potential%20clients%20with%20at%20least%20%2410%20million%20in%20cash%20or%20an%20easily%20liquidated%20asset%20class%2C%20like%20stocks%20and%20shares%2C%20who%20were%20interested%20in%20opening%20an%20account%20with%20us.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20majority%20of%20my%20clients%20were%20trying%20to%20preserve%20their%20wealth%2C%20but%20some%20were%20still%20trying%20to%20make%20money.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20the%20client%20structured%20their%20portfolio%20would%20depend%20on%20whether%20they%20were%20in%20wealth%20preservation%20or%20wealth%20accumulation%20mode%20and%20on%20their%20knowledge%20of%20different%20products.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ea68df3b-0bbf-473e-b02f-dba9f987d977%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3ENormal%20people%20can%20learn%20from%20the%20rich%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20Goldman%2C%20I%20made%20rich%20men%20richer%20every%20day%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20feel%20like%20I%20had%20a%20seat%20at%20the%20table.%20I%20wanted%20to%20use%20my%20skills%20for%20something%20more%20positive.%20I%20quit%20in%202018%20to%20start%20my%20own%20business%20in%202019.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20noticed%20there%20were%20things%20that%20wealthy%20people%20did%20to%20build%20wealth%20that%20were%20different%20from%20how%20normal%20people%20managed%20their%20money%2C%20such%20as%20their%20approach%20to%20savings%2C%20investments%2C%20and%20debt.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20philosophies%20I%20saw%20in%20terms%20of%20wealth%20building%20at%20Goldman%2C%20I'm%20trying%20to%20bring%20to%20my%20business%2C%20Propelle%2C%20a%20platform%20to%20help%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwomen-will-benefit-from-wealth-trends-millennials-boomers-investment-finance2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewomen%20close%20the%20investment%20gap%20with%20men%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221bae9cd2-e899-40d3-8c3a-6ac76bf5a079%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3ESaving%20money%20isn't%20enough%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20was%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs%2C%20I%20noticed%20we%20didn't%20have%20many%20women%20clients.%20I%20did%20some%20research%20and%20realized%20that%2C%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20women%20are%20good%20at%20saving%20money%20but%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F120ba6b9-b8f5-4000-a618-07c6f8f7d845%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enot%20investing%20it%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWomen%20are%20paid%20less%20and%20are%20often%20the%20ones%20who%20take%20time%20away%20from%20work%20to%20care%20for%20children%20or%20older%20relatives.%20The%20pension%20gap%20between%20men%20and%20women%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tuc.org.uk%2Fresearch-analysis%2Freports%2Fgender-pensions-gap%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSince%25202022%2520we%2520have%2520marked%2Cthe%2520way%2520through%2520the%2520year%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20UK%20is%2040%25%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Many%20women%20reach%20the%20later%20stages%20of%20their%20lives%2C%20and%20they%20don't%20have%20enough%20money%20to%20maintain%20their%20standard%20of%20living.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20wealth%20gap%20between%20men%20and%20women%20is%20big%2C%20and%20women%20must%20catch%20up.%20Why%20aren't%20we%20investing%20like%20the%20wealthy%20do%3F%20All%20my%20clients%20were%20investing%20in%20some%20way.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20worked%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs%2C%20I%20was%20focused%20on%20paying%20off%20my%20student%20loans%20and%20saving%20money.%20I%20realized%20the%20last%20place%20my%20money%20should%20be%20is%20sitting%20in%20the%20bank%2C%20doing%20nothing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20created%20an%20investment%20portfolio%2C%20like%20I%20would%20for%20my%20clients%2C%20and%20invested%20in%20real%20estate.%20That%20financial%20safety%20net%20helped%20me%20leave%20Goldman%20and%20start%20my%20own%20company.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInvesting%20is%20about%20having%20a%20long-term%20time%20horizon.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20get-rich-quick%20scheme.%20It's%20about%20thinking%20about%20the%20future%2C%20creating%20a%20plan%2C%20and%20investing%20steadily.%20I%20want%20women%20to%20get%20to%20the%20point%20where%20they%20are%20investing%20monthly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224ea6518e-f06d-4d9b-ad97-034cd20b8dac%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EInvest%20in%20alternatives%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20Goldman%20Sachs%2C%20there%20were%20different%20ways%20to%20create%20client%20portfolios.%20One%20strategy%20was%20called%20%26quot%3Bcore-satellite.%26quot%3B%20In%20the%20middle%2C%20they%20would%20have%20traditional%20investment%20classes%2C%20such%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-an-etf%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAn%2520exchange%252Dtraded%2520fund%2520(ETF%2Cliquid%2520as%2520some%2520mutual%2520funds.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eexchange-traded%20funds%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(ETFs).%20Around%20that%20core%20layer%2C%20there%20was%20a%20satellite%20layer%20of%20alternatives%2C%20which%20a%20lot%20of%20clients%20came%20to%20Goldman%20to%20access.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20investment%20platforms%20focus%20too%20much%20on%20traditional%20investments.%20Wealthy%20people%20are%20more%20able%20to%20take%20calculated%20risks%20because%20they%20have%20the%20tools%20and%20advisors%20at%20their%20disposal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20want%20women%20looking%20to%20start%20investing%20to%20have%20access%20to%20alternatives%2C%20too.%20For%20example%2C%20it%20could%20mean%20investing%20on%20a%20small%20scale%20in%20startups%2C%20art%2C%20or%20wine%20as%20non-traditional%20investments%20to%20have%20in%20their%20portfolio.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20not%20exactly%20the%20same%20as%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20everyday%20people%20should%20invest%20in%20hedge%20funds.%20But%20they%20could%20invest%20in%20similar%20things%2C%20such%20as%20startups%2C%20where%20the%20risk%20and%20reward%20can%20be%20higher.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere's%20generally%20a%20lower%20minimum%20investment%20for%20investing%20in%20startups%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0as%20little%20as%20%2420%20sometimes.%20It's%20slightly%20different%20from%20investing%20%2410%20million%20like%20a%20Goldman%20Sachs%20client%20might%2C%20but%20the%20principle%20is%20the%20same.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20Propelle%2C%20my%20investment%20app%2C%20the%20plan%20for%20users%20is%20to%20focus%20on%20having%20both%20traditional%20and%20alternative%20investments.%20It's%20about%20taking%20a%20calculated%20risk%2C%20not%20a%20blind%20risk.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ec7a853c-0759-4341-ac7e-93c9b6bc4004%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EDebt%20isn't%20always%20bad%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20noticed%20wealthy%20people%20are%20good%20at%20making%20money%20with%20money%20that%20isn't%20theirs%20through%20borrowing.%20It's%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20drivers%20for%20building%20wealth.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20look%20at%20debt%20as%20financial%20engineering.%20It%20is%20a%20tool.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20can%20use%20debt%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20generate%20wealth%2C%20but%20everyday%20people%20don't%20see%20it%20that%20way.%20Many%20people%20are%20terrified%20of%20debt.%20My%20mom%20is%20one%20of%20them.%20She%20wants%20to%20be%20able%20to%20pay%20off%20her%20mortgage%2C%20and%20she%20doesn't%20want%20a%20credit%20card.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20encouraged%20her%20to%20think%20of%20a%20mortgage%20as%20a%20tool.%20An%20example%20is%20if%20you%20release%20equity%20from%20a%20property%20you%20own%20and%20pay%206%25%20on%20the%20borrowed%20money.%20You%20could%20use%20that%20money%20to%20invest%20in%20a%20property%20development%20project%20with%20projected%2020%25%20returns.%20The%2014%25%20difference%20would%20be%20income%2C%20not%20considering%20taxes.%20It%20depends%20on%20interest%20rates%2C%20but%20that's%20a%20no-brainer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERisk%20is%20clearly%20a%20factor%20because%20the%206%25%20interest%20rate%20is%20guaranteed%20however%2C%20the%2020%25%20returns%20aren't.%20A%20clear%20plan%20for%20expected%20returns%20and%20timelines%20or%20a%20contingency%20plan%20is%20important%20if%20you're%20taking%20on%20risk.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI've%20seen%20a%20lot%20of%20wealthy%20clients%20borrow%20money%20against%20their%20stock%20portfolio%20and%20use%20it%20to%20invest%20in%20something%20else.%20It%20could%20be%20on%20stocks%20and%20shares%20or%20property.%20You're%20hopefully%20generating%20a%20return%20on%20your%20stocks%20and%20returns%20on%20your%20second%20investment.%20You%20started%20with%20one%20pot%20of%20money%2C%20and%20now%20you%20have%20two%20generating%20returns%20for%20you%20while%20paying%20a%20lower%20interest%20rate%20on%20your%20debt%20than%20your%20returns.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWealthy%20people%20are%20doing%20that%2C%20just%20on%20a%20different%20level.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20works%20if%20the%20market%20is%20growing%20throughout%20your%20investments.%20If%20the%20market%20falls%20and%20you%20have%20a%20loan%2C%20you'll%20still%20need%20to%20make%20payments.%20It's%20great%20to%20make%20your%20money%20work%20as%20hard%20as%20possible%2C%20but%20you%20need%20to%20ensure%20you're%20taking%20calculated%20risks%20and%20have%20contingency%20plans.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cf46afc1-44c1-4325-8a4a-78b9d67a5458%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv