0Prima's%20rendition%20of%20%26quot%3BSummer%3A%20The%20Donna%20Summer%20Musical%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20ended%20its%20stint%20on%20Broadway%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20in%20August%2C%20Norwegian%20replaced%20the%20impressive%20show%20with%20its%20own%20dance%20performance%20%26quot%3BBossa%20Nova%20Beat.%26quot%3B%20(Prima%20still%20shows%20Norwegian's%20take%20on%20the%20recognizable%20%26quot%3BThe%20Price%20Is%20Right%20Live%26quot%3B%20game%20show.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBreakaway%20had%20the%20next-best%20alternatives%20to%20Broadway%20productions%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BBroadway%20Cabaret%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20covered%20well-known%20musical%20hits%2C%20and%20%26quot%3BBurn%20the%20Floor%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20song-and-dance%20spectacular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20these%20were%20the%20only%20two%20main%20productions%20shows%20on%20Rains'%20weeklong%20sailing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThankfully%2C%20both%20ships%20had%20smaller%20alternative%20entertainment%20venues.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20amenities%20inside%20Norwegian%20Cruise%20Line's%20Norwegian%20Prima%20cruise%20ship.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67002d1e198738e3a70e5fc1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20venues%20on%20Prime.%3Cp%3EBrittany%20Chang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrima%20and%20Breakaway%20had%20Syd%20Norman's%20Pour%20House%2C%20the%20go-to%20for%20dancing%20to%20covers%20of%20rock%20classics.%20Both%20ships%20also%20flexed%20comedy%20venues%2C%20albeit%20Prima's%20was%20exclusively%20improv%2C%20while%20Breakaway's%20had%20dueling%20pianos.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnly%20the%20latter%20had%20the%20circus-like%20Spiegel%20Tent%2C%20which%20hosted%20live%20music%20and%20Bingo%20programming.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBut%20both%20ships%20had%20bet