e%20attracted%20to%20the%20town's%20affordable%20living%2C%20mild%20weather%2C%20and%20expat%20community.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESince%20moving%2C%20they%20say%20they're%20happier%2C%20and%20their%20lives%20are%20much%20less%20stressful.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2014%2C%202022%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40kellesparta%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKelle%20Sparta%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20Jeff%20Brandon%2C%20set%20foot%20in%20Boquete%2C%20Panama%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20visit%20to%20the%20small%20central%20Panamanian%20town%20wasn't%20for%20vacation.%20They%20didn't%20have%20immediate%20plans%20to%20explore%20nearby%20coffee%20farms%20or%20to%20hike%20Panama's%20largest%20volcano.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Sparta%2C%2054%2C%20and%20Brandon%2C%2041%2C%20landed%20in%20Boquete%2C%20they%20arrived%20sight%20unseen%20at%20the%20place%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboomer-moving-texas-panama-retirement-cheaper-tourism-weather-social-security-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethey'd%20call%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20foreseeable%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b45c55d3-6f31-4e7b-829b-fbcf3585fb87%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20couple%20left%20the%20US%20in%20search%20of%20a%20less%20stressful%20environment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESparta%20told%20Business%20Insider%20she%20was%20used%20to%20moving.%20Raised%20in%20a%20military%20family%2C%20she%20said%20she's%20moved%2040%20times%20in%20her%2054-year%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20the%20couple%20moved%20to%20Richmond%2C%20Virginia%2C%20from%20Boston.%20They%20were%20searching%20for%20a%20place%20where%20they%20could%20afford%20property%20and%20find%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20beginning%20of%202020%2C%20they%20purchased%20a%20house%20just%20as%20COVID-19%20arrived%20in%20the%20US%20and%20lockdowns%20started.%20Sparta%20and%20Brandon%20didn't%20have