she%20was%20confident%20and%20carried%20herself%20exceptionally%20well.%20She%20is%20a%20true%20inspiration%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Priyatama%20is%20at%20peace%20with%20herself%20and%20is%20slowly%20taking%20steps%20to%20heal%20her%20trauma%20with%20the%20help%20of%20therapy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20I%20would%20shiver%20and%20feel%20cold%20just%20thinking%20about%20those%20incidents.%20I%E2%80%99m%20working%20my%20way%20out%20of%20that.%20My%20body%20is%20just%20a%20body%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20my%20identity.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20ever%20let%20anyone%20make%20you%20feel%20less%20than%20you%20are%20because%20of%20the%20abuse%20inflicted%20on%20you.%20We%20are%20more%20than%20our%20bodies%2C%E2%80%9D%20Priyatama%20says.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20creating%20a%20better%20India%20for%20women%2C%20Priyatama%20emphasises%20that%20it%20all%20begins%20at%20home%20and%20how%20we%20raise%20our%20children%2C%20especially%20boys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20must%20raise%20boys%20and%20girls%20equally.%20Let%20your%20boys%20also%20express%20their%20emotions.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20chide%20them%20when%20they%20cry%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%98Why%20are%20you%20crying%20like%20a%20girl%3F%E2%80%99%20Let%20go%20of%20these%20biases.%20Protect%20your%20children%20and%20make%20them%20mentally%20sound%20and%20strong.%20When%20boys%20are%20sensitive%20and%20in%20touch%20with%20their%20emotions%2C%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20harm%20girls%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Even%20if%20one%20child%20is%20saved%2C%20I%20am%20happy%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriyatama%20believes%20that%20it%20is%20important%20to%20teach%20children%20the%20concepts%20of%20good%20and%20bad%20touch%20and%20create%20an%20open%20environ