20(Rajbari)%20boasts%2014%20rooms%20which%20can%20accommodate%20a%20total%20of%2040%20guests.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20delve%20further%20into%20history%2C%20Pallab%20draws%20attention%20to%20the%20notable%20parallels%20between%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%E2%80%99s%20functions%20and%20those%20of%20the%20palaces%20in%20England.%20%E2%80%9CAround%201924%2C%20the%20house%20had%20200%20guards.%20There%20was%20also%20the%20%E2%80%98Changing%20of%20the%20Guard%E2%80%99%20ceremony%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F48468%2Flieutenant-colonel-sophia-qureshi-indian-army%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emilitary%20drills%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20were%2034%20gardeners%2C%20innumerable%20staff%20and%20nine%20functioning%20kitchens.%E2%80%9D%20He%20laughs%20as%20he%20recounts%20the%20famous%20tea%20parties%20held%20at%20Cossimbazar%20Palace.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20crockery%20and%20cutlery%20for%20these%20were%20imported%20from%20England!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20in%201947%2C%20as%20India%20got%20freedom%2C%20and%20the%20estate%20system%20was%20abolished%20soon%20after%2C%20the%20fate%20of%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20took%20a%20drastic%20turn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FVZaaCzClgxA%3Fsi%3D1WO9zmnnvPyi5MQ3%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20assets%20in%20our%20family%20were%20self-earned%20over%2010%20generations%3B%20they%20were%20not%20grants%20from%20the%20Government.%20But%20everything%20went%20away%20without%20a%20single%20%3Cem%3Epaisa%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Indian%20currency%20denomination)%3B%20they%20were%20auctioned.%20I%20have%20heard%20stories%20of%20how%20everything%20vanished%20overnight%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pallab%20laments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20grandfather%20would%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98From%20a%20king%2C%20I%20became%20a%20pauper%E2%80%99.%20The%20staff%20at%20the%20estate%2C%20the%20Government%2C%20and%20the%20system%20turned%20against%20him%20as%20dues%2C%20penalties%2C%20arrears%2C%20and%20international%20income%20issues%20began%20to%20surface.%20It%20was%20a%20miserable%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20solution%20that%20Raja%20Kamalaranjan%20Roy%20saw%20was%20to%20leave%20behind%20his%20Murshidabad%20house%20and%20shift%20to%20Kolkata%20with%20his%20family.%20It%20was%20here%20that%20Pallab%E2%80%99s%20parents%20married%20and%20a%20major%20part%20of%20his%20life%20would%20be%20spent%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333208%2Fwhere-to-eat-in-kolkata-classics-best-heritage-eateries-map-anindya-basu-dolon-dutta%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98City%20of%20Joy%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-4-1726573572.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22While%20the%20Roys%20pride%20themselves%20on%20their%20ancestral%20legacy%20that%20is%20now%20a%20heritage%20hotel%2C%20they%20also%20continue%20to%20lead%20their%20confectionery%20brand%20'Sugar%20and%20Spice'%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-4-1726573572.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-4-1726573572-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-4-1726573572-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.c