3Cp%3EThrough%20collaborations%20with%20organisations%20such%20as%20Save%20The%20Children%20and%20UNICEF%2C%20she%20spearheaded%20initiatives%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20the%20dangers%20of%20early%20marriage%20and%20empower%20young%20girls%20to%20reclaim%20their%20futures.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20working%20with%20them%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20prevent%2012%20child%20marriages%20in%20Khagaria%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20her%20unwavering%20commitment%20and%20tireless%20efforts%20were%20recognised%20on%20a%20global%20stage%20when%20she%20was%20honoured%20by%20the%20United%20Nations%20in%20Geneva%2C%20Switzerland.%20This%20prestigious%20award%20not%20only%20acknowledged%20her%20remarkable%20achievements%20but%20also%20served%20as%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20power%20of%20one%20individual%E2%80%99s%20determination%20to%20effect%20positive%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Roshni%20has%20developed%20a%20strong%20base%20in%20schools%20and%20communities%20by%20creating%2015%20adolescent%20girls%20groups%20in%20villages%20such%20as%20Simalwari%2C%20Bagalwari%2C%20Maheshbhatna%2C%20Kochadhaman%2C%20Bahadurganj%2C%20Dighalbank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Froshni-child-marriage-1-1727791886.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Roshni's%20unwavering%20commitment%20and%20tireless%20efforts%20have%20been%20recognised%20on%20global%20stage.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Froshni-child-marriage-1-1727791886.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Froshni-child-marriage-1-1727791886-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Froshni-child-marriage-1-1727791886-500x262.jpg%2050