Lives%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20coastal%20villages%20of%20Karanj%20and%20Katpor%20in%20Surat%E2%80%99s%20Hansot%20block%20are%20enveloped%20by%20a%20thriving%20mangrove%20forest%2C%20a%20lush%20sea%20of%20green.%20Once%20nearly%20barren%20wasteland%20just%2015%20years%20ago%2C%20these%20areas%20have%20since%20transformed%2C%20offering%20villagers%20a%20sustainable%20livelihood%20and%20improving%20their%20economic%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20growth%20of%20mangroves%20has%20helped%20increase%20the%20income%20of%20both%20farmers%20and%20fishermen%2C%20with%20improved%20crop%20yields%20leading%20to%20higher%20profits.%20What%20was%20once%20a%20barren%20area%20has%20now%20become%20a%20thriving%20ecosystem%2C%20benefiting%20not%20only%20the%20community%20but%20also%20the%20environment.%20The%20mangroves%20have%20even%20attracted%20new%20species%20of%20birds%20and%20animals%20to%20the%20villages%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20biodiversity%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Babubhai%20Rathod%2C%20former%20%3Cem%3Esarpanch%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20a%20resident%20of%20Karanj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20mangrove%20plantation%20was%20carried%20out%20by%20L%26amp%3BT%20as%20part%20of%20their%20Blue%20Carbon%20initiative%20%E2%80%94%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Gujarat%20Ecology%20Commission%20(GEC)%20%E2%80%94%20and%20implemented%20through%20a%20community-based%20village%20organisation%20across%20more%20than%20150%20hectares%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompleted%20in%202015%2C%20the%20mangroves%20have%20since%20become%20vital%20to%20the%20villagers%2C%20providing%20resources%20such%20as%20fodder%2C%20fuelwood%2C%20and%20supporting%20fishing%20activities.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20mangroves%20act%20as%20a%20natural%20barrier%2C%20preventing%20saltwater%20from%20encroaching%20on%20farmlands%20and%20protecting%20crops%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20improves%20crop%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EL%26amp%3BT%E2%80%99s%20focus%2C%20in%20line%20with%20ESG%20(Environmental%2C%20Social%2C%20and%20Governance)%20parameters%2C%20is%20to%20minimise%20the%20environmental%20impact%20of%20their%20manufacturing%2C%20operations%2C%20and%20processes.%20Through%20green%20initiatives%20like%20the%20Blue%20Carbon%20project%2C%20it%20is%20actively%20working%20towards%20achieving%20carbon%20neutrality%20by%202040.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20waves%20%E2%80%94%20environmentally%20and%20economically%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangroves%20are%20vital%20tropical%20plants%20that%20thrive%20in%20coastal%20ecosystems%20under%20conditions%20most%20timber%20cannot%20tolerate.%20They%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20storing%20large%20amounts%20of%20carbon%20and%20protecting%20shorelines%20and%20their%20inhabitants%20from%20damaging%20winds%2C%20waves%2C%20and%20floods.%20Additionally%2C%20mangroves%20help%20prevent%20salinity%20and%20seawater%20intrusion%20into%20agricultural%20areas%2C%20improving%20crop%20quality%20and%20enabling%20farmers%20to%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%204000px)%20100vw%2C%204000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG_0780_11zon-1727781273.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Picture%20before%20the%20mangrove%20plantation.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG_0780_11zon-1727781273.jpg%204000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG_0780_11zon-1727781273-300x123.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG_0780_11zon-1727781273-500x205.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG_0780_11zon-1727781273-768x314.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FIMG_0780_11zon-1727781273-1536x629.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebett