ides%20the%20standard%20equipment%20they%20are%20given%2C%20Drishti%20Marine%20has%20also%20employed%20dogs%20to%20assist%20them%20in%20their%20rescue%20and%20monitoring%20efforts.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Rajiv%20claims%2C%20%E2%80%9CDrishti%20Marine%20has%20also%20introduced%20the%20first%20of%20its%20kind%20initiative%20in%20Asia%20%E2%80%94%20expertly%20trained%20dogs%20called%20%E2%80%98Paw%20Squad%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20to%20bolster%20their%20rescue%20efforts.%20These%20dogs%2C%20accompanied%20by%20their%20handlers%20are%20trained%20in%20patrolling%20and%20detecting%20people%20in%20distress.%20Drishti%20Marine%20lifesavers%20are%20also%20the%20first%20responders%20to%20any%20marine%20strandings%20and%20are%20trained%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20Wildlife%20Protection%20Act%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPaw-Patrol-Drishti-Marine-1727448965.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20member%20of%20the%20'Paw%20Squad'%20on%20patrol.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPaw-Patrol-Drishti-Marine-1727448965.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPaw-Patrol-Drishti-Marine-1727448965-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPaw-Patrol-Drishti-Marine-1727448965-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPaw-Patrol-Drishti-Marine-1727448965-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPaw-Patrol-Drishti-Marine-1727448965-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367907%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20member%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Paw%